  card_001,news,medium,"What is the significance of Envision Radiology's acquisition of Rezolut?","This acquisition represents consolidation in the imaging industry, likely increasing Envision Radiology's market share and potentially impacting referral patterns and access to imaging services in the acquired regions.",Google News Radiology;news;industry consolidation;referral patterns,
  card_002,news,medium,"Why is the search for a new editor for 'Radiology: Cardiothoracic Imaging' important?","The journal is a prominent publication, and a new editor can bring updated perspectives and priorities, potentially influencing research and clinical practice in cardiothoracic imaging.",Google News Radiology;news;journal editing;cardiothoracic imaging;RSNA,
  card_003,ir,hard,"What is the main clinical implication of the FDA petition regarding cervical spine fracture detection on CT?","The petition proposes an alternative approach for detecting cervical spine fractures on CT, potentially leading to changes in CT protocols for trauma patients and improved detection of subtle injuries.",link.springer.com;FDA;cervical spine;CT;trauma,
  card_004,msk,medium,"What is the focus of the study on prostate volume, PI-RADS, and PSA density?","The study investigates the relationship between prostate volume, PI-RADS category, and optimal PSA-density thresholds for prostate biopsy, aiming to refine current guidelines and potentially reduce unnecessary biopsies.",Eur. Radiology;prostate cancer;PSA density;PI-RADS;biopsy,
  card_005,ir,medium,"How does digital variance angiography impact radiation dose during prostatic artery embolization?","A prospective study shows that digital variance angiography can reduce radiation dose during prostatic artery embolization by up to 80%, offering a safer alternative for this procedure.",Eur. Radiology;interventional radiology;radiation dose;prostatic artery embolization;digital variance angiography

